===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{lb|en|obsolete}} An [[inscription]] in stone.
# A [[brief]] but [[witty]] [[saying]].
# A [[short]], witty or [[pithy]] [[poem]].
#: ''When an '''epigram''' one's composin',''
#: ''brevity is key,''
#: ''of stanzas: one should be chosen,
#: ''and of lines: one more than three.''

